This paper discusses the design specifications and suitability of different LPWAN solutions for IoT applications, which falls under the category of networked systems and communication (cs.NI). It also touches upon the challenges and potential research directions for LPWANs, which could be relevant to information theory (cs.IT), control systems (cs.SY), cryptography and security (cs.CR), and multiagent systems (cs.MA).
